{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Region Renamer\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Given a media item selection containing two or more items:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li1080 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Moves all selected media items within each track to the left, snapping them together while keeping their order.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li1080 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Uses the leftmost selected item per track as the anchor.\sa180\par}
}

