{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Extend Region Bounds to Nearby Items\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Given a timeline selection that overlaps any region boundary, this script will extend the region(s) boundary or boundaries to the nearest item.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Useful when working with many variations, so you avoid having to manually extend the boundary to fit within the items you're playing.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Recommended to add this script to the 'Ruler/arrange context' menu.\sa180\par}
}

